<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7929544>
    dc:description "FIGURES 26 & 27. Alloglossidium raychaudhurii (Agarwal & Kumar, 1983) n. comb. and Anomalomacroderoiditrema keni (Agarwal & Agarwal, 1984) n. gen., n. comb. 26. Al. raychaudhurii (syn. Pseudoparamacroderoides raychaudhurii Agarwal & Kumar, 1983), ventral view, redrawn from Agarwal & Kumar (1983, fig. 1A). 27. An. keni (syn. Pseudoparamacroderoides keni Agarwal & Agarwal, 1984), dorsal view, redrawn from Agarwal & Agarwal (1984, fig. 1A). Abbreviations: AT, anterior testis; BS, body spines; Ce, cecum; CP, cirrus-pouch; ED, ejaculatory duct; Eg, egg; EP, excretory pore; Es, esophagus; EV, excretory vesicle; GP, genital pore; LC, Laurer’s canal; OC, ôtype complex; OS, oral sucker; Ov, ovary; Ph, pharynx; PP, pars prostatica; Pr.Ph, prepharynx; PT, posterior testis; SR, seminal receptacle; SV, seminal vesicle; Ut, uterus; VD, vitelline duct; VF, vitelline follicle; VS, ventral sucker. Scale bars: Fig. 26 = 500 µm; Fig. 27 = 300 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7929544/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

